   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table id="table_trd_wd2_lcc" class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_mtp_yd2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock! </b>Contact with live components poses a
                              risk of serious injury or even death!<ul id="ul_hfp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, switch off the electric power supply.
                                    Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout.</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_irx_v15_jcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Life threatening hazard due to a falling vertical carriage!</b>The
                              unsecured vertical carriage can fall down and cause serious injury or
                              even death! <ul id="ul_afm_jg2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Always make sure that the safety bolts of the vertical carriage
                                    are properly installed before carrying out work on / near the
                                    carriage</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_ppy_lg2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of injury from improperly performed maintenance!</b>Improper
                              maintenance can result in serious personal injury or material
                              damage!</p>
                           <ul id="ul_ifp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, ensure that you have sufficient space!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Handle open, sharp-edged components with care!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Pay attention to cleanliness and orderliness at the place of work!
                                 Loose components and tools lying around are a potential cause of
                                 accidents!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Install all components correctly. Observe the prescribed bolt
                                 tightening torques! Secure the bolts with bolt locking com- pound
                                 (e.g. Weicon AN 302-43 (blue)) “medium strength”!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Secure components so that they cannot fall down or fall over!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Operating elements of the Emergency Stop system must be freely
                                 accessible!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Operate the machine only when all the safety devices, e.g. safety
                                 fence, light barriers and safety bolts are installed and fully
                                 functional!</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_eqf_pg2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Risk of injury from stored pneumatic energy! </b>Pneumatic energy
                              may be stored in the machine that can lead to uncontrolled movements
                              of components and injuries!<ul id="ul_fvm_qg2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout of the system.
                                    Only then start the maintenance work!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_lqw_rg2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of crushing! </b>There are several crushing points on the
                              machine that can cause injuries!</p>
                           <ul id="ul_jfp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Do not reach between the following points: </li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the steel housing</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the lifting mast</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">the locking pins and the container</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the horizontal carriage!</li>
                           </ul>
                           <ul id="ul_kfp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">No person is allowed inside the safety fence area when the machine
                                 is switched on!</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_ezt_5g2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Danger due to non-observance of the prohibition of transporting
                                 persons! </b>The MSK transfer system can pose a serious risk in the
                              event of non-compliance and/or circumvention of the prohibition of
                              trans- porting persons.</p>
                           <ul id="ul_lfp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Only operate the transfer system when all safety devices are in
                                 place and in proper working condition, such as the programmed
                                 safety interlocks and physical E-Stops.</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">No persons are allowed on the transfer system!</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_drz_gh2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Risk of injury due to stored hydraulic energy!</b> Hydraulic
                              energy can be stored in the machine and cause the un- controlled
                              movement of components, which can lead to severe in- juries!</p>
                           <ul id="ul_mfp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Switch off the MSK system, as explained in this document.</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Do not begin maintenance work until then!</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_c2y_jh2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Risk of injury due to laser radiation!</b> Laser radiation can
                              cause serious eye damage. Connie needs to follow-up with Steven and
                              Kirk. We may need additional training.</p>
                           <ul id="ul_nfp_zh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Do not look into the laser beam!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">If it is not possible to avoid looking directly into the laser
                                 beam (e.g., during maintenance work), suitable eye protection must
                                 be worn.</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="caution" id="note_xbw_mh2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock !</b> Parts of the machine may still be
                              live even when the emergency stop switch has been pressed! </p>
                           <ul id="ul_rc2_qh2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Do not touch live parts and leads!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Observe the instructions in the operating manual!</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
